The use of expert preferences and active ranking to refine the policy return is a technique that falls under the category of machine learning. Therefore, the most likely sub-category is cs.LG (Machine Learning). Additionally, the paper discusses the application of this technique in swarm robotics, which falls under the category of robotics (cs.RO). The paper also mentions the use of inverse reinforcement learning, which is a subfield of artificial intelligence (cs.AI). The paper also discusses the use of policy search, which is a technique used in control systems (cs.SY). Finally, the paper presents experiments on two testbeds, which is a common practice in mathematical optimization (cs.MA).
